	(176, 2, '2013-01-07 06:56:08', '2013-01-07 14:56:08', '<p class="MsoNormal">Whilst we are still an invite-only service, we at Enclothed are thrilled by the number of men asking for specific style advice. One question in particular has really stood out: “Are coloured chino’s only for summer?” Our answer – definitely not!</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">The chino not only makes any man more noticeable to the endless jeans wearers, but is also undeniably more comfortable than many trousers.</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">BROGUES AND CHINOS</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">Match your chinos with a pair of brogues and immediately take away any notion of summer and welcome a more sophisticated look. Try to match your brogues and belt just like Aaron from team Enclothed.</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><img alt="image" src="http://media.tumblr.com/daf4df6db56d4a9eb5ed88060828257b/tumblr_inline_mg448dwyxH1rd6zrs.png"/></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">CHINOS AND TRAINERS</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">For a more casual look, do it like the boss himself Jay Z by pairing simple and clean trainers with a pair of chinos. Navy trainers work well with most coloured chinos.</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><img alt="image" src="http://media.tumblr.com/6d56a8a17bb3824f4694343195a27665/tumblr_inline_mg3zw4yZmb1rd6zrs.jpg"/></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">(image source: mydaily)</p>', 'CHINOS IN WINTER', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'chinos-in-winter', '', '', '2013-01-07 06:56:08', '2013-01-07 14:56:08', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/39661330346', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(177, 2, '2013-01-07 06:55:11', '2013-01-07 14:55:11', '<p>Clothes have the power to turn heads your way and make you feel appropriate in different occasions, but did you know they can also influence the way you think, feel and behave.</p>\n<p>HUH?</p>\n<p>Have you ever thought why when we wear certain clothes such as a suit, we feel we are ready to take on different roles and push ourselves beyond our basic abilities. This phenomenon is called the “ENCLOTHED COGINITION”. Studies show, <span>If you wear a white coat that you believe belongs to a doctor, your ability to pay attention increases sharply. But if you wear the same white coat believing it belongs to a painter, you will show no such improvement.</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<p>So not only is shopping inconvenient, now we have to worry about whether our clothes might ruin our day?</p>\n<p>HOW TO MAKE ENCLOTHED COGNITION WORK FOR YOU</p>\n<p>AT WORK</p>\n<p>You can earn at least 5% more than the other guy simply by looking sharp according to a study by the American Economic Review. Clothes sell confidence, so suit up or if more casual stock up on some crisp shirts, a blazer, chinos and some statement shoes.</p>\n<p><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/632a7d66d166ce7b4ac5fda8cc00dc3e/tumblr_inline_mg44y2SoEP1rd6zrs.png"/></p>\n<p>AT THE GYM</p>\n<p>Ditch your baggy jumpers and get some real sports gear. Wearing the latest sporting attire has positive associations with fitness levels and performance. It could make you work harder, run further and reach your goals faster.</p>\n<p>ON YOUR FIRST DATE</p>\n<p>Here is where it gets a bit complicated, there’s no quick trick. Wear whatever makes you comfortable and best expresses your personality.</p>\n<p>Although we’d like to claim we have deep philosophical tendencies and named the company after this scientific phenomenon, it sadly was as simple as “it’s clothes enclosed in a box’. But no one has to know that….</p>', 'CLOTHES REALLY DO MAKE THE MAN', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'clothes-really-do-make-the-man', '', '', '2013-01-07 06:55:11', '2013-01-07 14:55:11', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/39667107243', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(178, 2, '2013-01-04 07:15:36', '2013-01-04 15:15:36', '<blockquote>A man should look as if he bought his clothes with intelligence, put them on with care, and then forgotten all about them.</blockquote>\n    <p>- Hardy Aimes</p>\n<div></div>', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'a-man-should-look-as-if-he-bought-his-clothes-with-intelligence-put-them-on-with-care-and-then-forgotten-all-about-them', '', '', '2013-01-04 07:15:36', '2013-01-04 15:15:36', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/39658708789', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(179, 2, '2013-01-04 06:44:00', '2013-01-04 14:44:00', '<p class="MsoNormal">Enclothed is a premium online personal styling service aimed to solve one of life&#8217;s simple problems - most men do not have the time or desire to go shopping in stores or online. Shopping is inconvenient, shops are crowded, queues are long and sifting through endless rails is frustrating. With Enclothed, men get the clothes they want, from the brands they like, without going shopping. We work with some of the best brands around so you can be sure to receive a trunk filled with clothes from your favourite brands, alongside some others we know you’ll love. With our combination of premium  brands and exceptional personal stylist, we deliver a personal and convenient service that helps men look great with no effort.</p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal">HOW DOES IT WORK?</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">Men sign up to our service and create a profile by answering some questions for their personal stylist to handpick clothing especially for them. Their trunk is delivered to their door for them try on clothing in the comfort of their home. What they love they keep, what they don&#8217;t - we pick up for free. There is no added charge for our service, delivery or returns. Keep your wardrobe updated and in style with no effort.</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">We are currently in Beta mode and are giving access to a number of selected people so that our public launch is the premium service it is destined to be. However, don’t let that stop you from getting to know our stylists. If you’d like to know more, email us at <a href="mailto:help@enclothed.co.uk">help@enclothed.co.uk</a> but stick around as we’ll be posting some exciting stuff that’ll make your lifestyle easier.</p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal">WHY BOTHER SHOPPING AGAIN?</p>', 'WE ARE PROUD TO ANNOUNCE ENCLOTHED', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'we-are-proud-to-announce-enclothed', '', '', '2013-01-04 06:44:00', '2013-01-04 14:44:00', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/39657279672', 0, 'post', '', 0),
